  "title": "Freight Documentation Manager",
  "description": "<p>Our group is involved in the import, sale and installation of new tyres, and the export of waste tyres and waste paper. </p><p><br /></p><p>We are looking for a freight documentation manager for our business.</p><p><br /></p><p>Job Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Coordination with customers and suppliers/vendors</li><li>Handles cargo documentation</li><li>Declare permits and handle shipping documentation</li><li>Liaise with shipping lines, haulers </li><li>Handle cross border transport and documentation</li><li>Handle and check letters of credit and liasing with our banks in respect thereto</li><li>Prepare invoices and packing lists, coordinate with surveyors where required.</li><li>Keep proper records as required by our Finance Department</li><li>All other administrative work as assigned</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><p>- Bachelor's degree</p><p>- At least 4 years’ experience, preferably in tyre or waste paper industry</p><p>- Able to handle full set of shipping documentation and letter of credit procedure</p><p>- Experience handling procedures for export of goods to Malaysia and Indonesia an advantage<br /><br />- Willing to do shift work if stocks due to arrive after usual hours.</p><p></p><p>Kindly email to contact@cbhtyres.com with expected salary. Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
